            "id": 6020165,
            "title": "《異動股》中芯吐逾2%,傳三星已成功量產2納米GAA製程晶片",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社12日專訊》中芯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00981:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00981\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00981-HK</a>)H股現價跌2.2%,報40.75元,該股成交約3532萬股,涉資14.46億元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><tr></tr></section><section><p class=\"\">2600晶片在5月的試產階段遭到挑戰,有指這款2納米GAA製程晶片優良率在今年初僅得30%,但在上個月起已經邁向50%,有可能可以在先進製程比拼上媲美,甚至超越台積電。</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><tr></tr></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">優良率,盡量降低成本,並挑戰能進一步降低成本的70%優良率進發。三星早在第一季財報強調穩定2納米GAA製程晶片的優良率為目前首要任務,爭取下半年全面量產。但據擊韓媒所報道的進度,三星大有可能已提前量產Exynos　2600。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><tr></tr></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">　Elite　Gen　2進行2　納米製程代工,但尚未獲得官方確認。</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　中資晶片股普遍回吐;華虹(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01347:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01347\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01347-HK</a>)跌3.1%,報29.9元;上海復旦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01385:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01385\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01385-HK</a>)跌1.7%,報28.1元;英諾賽科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02577:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02577\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02577-HK</a>)跌2.4%,報</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">36.05元;晶門(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02878:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02878\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02878-HK</a>)跌1.1%,報0.45元;宏光半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06908:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06908\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06908-HK</a>)跌3.8%,報0.51元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　現時,恒生指數報24110,跌256點或跌1.1%,主板成交近2021億元。國企指數報8759,跌105點或跌1.2%。恒生科技指數報5349,跌101點或跌1.9%。即月期指新報24080,跌263點,低水31點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>中芯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00981:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00981\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00981-HK</a>)</td><td>40.75元</td><td>跌2.16%</td></tr><tr><td>華虹(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01347:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01347\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01347-HK</a>)</td><td>29.90元</td><td>跌3.08%</td></tr><tr><td>上海復旦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01385:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01385\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01385-HK</a>)</td><td>28.10元</td><td>跌1.75%</td></tr><tr><td>英諾賽科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02577:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02577\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02577-HK</a>)</td><td>36.05元</td><td>跌2.44%</td></tr><tr><td>中電華大科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00085:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00085\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00085-HK</a>)</td><td>1.48元</td><td>無升跌</td></tr><tr><td>晶門(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02878:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02878\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02878-HK</a>)</td><td>0.45元</td><td>跌1.10%</td></tr><tr><td>貝克微(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02149:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02149\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02149-HK</a>)</td><td>74.35元</td><td>升6.21%</td></tr><tr><td>芯智控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02166:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02166\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02166-HK</a>)</td><td>1.72元</td><td>升1.18%</td></tr><tr><td>宏光半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06908:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06908\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06908-HK</a>)</td><td>0.51元</td><td>跌3.77%</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　(hc)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
